          <title>DJI Mavic 4 Pro Leaked Image Hints at Imminent Launch</title>
          <description><![CDATA[A leaked image of the DJI Mavic 4 Pro suggests its launch might not be too far away, with a rumored date of April 20, 2025. The image appears to show a reworked propeller design and a physically larger camera module.]]></description>
